.av93VnBkT8rC6BfwHXXl .ccHDoQWfCQ0wpKNe51Og {
  position: relative;

  width: 20px;

  border-color: #ffc107;
  /* 金色边框 */
}
/* 添加对号 */
.av93VnBkT8rC6BfwHXXl .ccHDoQWfCQ0wpKNe51Og:after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  display: none;
}
.av93VnBkT8rC6BfwHXXl input:checked + .ccHDoQWfCQ0wpKNe51Og:after {
  display: block;
  left: 50%;
  top: 50%;
